40
00:03:20,017 --> 00:03:22,585
<i>- Bunga Seruni?
-  Kau berkebun, Vic?</i>

41
00:03:22,637 --> 00:03:24,037
<i>Aku sedang mengisi laporan.</i>

42
00:03:24,105 --> 00:03:25,855
<i>Anak umur 11 tahun
